data.text: WSBR (740 AM) is a radio station broadcasting a business News Talk Information format. Licensed to Boca Raton, Florida, USA, the station serves the West Palm Beach/Boca Raton radio markets, with the Miami/Fort. Lauderdale market as a secondary. The station is currently owned by Beasley Broadcast Group, Inc., doing business as Beasley Media Group, LLC.
